-- Kraus-Maffei Wegmann Sees Defense Orders Drop, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   S h e e n a g h   M a t t h e w s
-- 2012-02-06T06:35:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-06/kraus-maffei-wegmann-sees-defense-orders-drop-handelsblatt-says.html
Krauss-Maffei Wegmann GmbH said the
defense industry is seeing a drop in orders as the U.S. and
European governments cut spending,  Handelsblatt  said, citing in
an interview with Chief Executive Officer Frank Haun.  The company sees potential for growth in countries such as
Brazil and  Chile , Haun said, according to the German newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sheenagh Matthews in Frankfurt at 
 smatthews6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
